Fixes to be made in the future:
- openNumberFormat does not allow to set all the parameters to unum_open (loss of functionality).
- formatIntegral, formatRealFrac do not allow to set all parameters to unum_format (loss of functionality).
- openDateFormat does not allow to set all the parameters to udat_open (loss of functionality).
- formatDate does not allow to set all the parameters to udat_format (loss of functionality).
- Modules NumberFormatting, DateTimeFormatting, Calendars, Locales are incomplete.
- Documentation is incomplete at least in NumberFormatting, Locales.
